title: Research the latest advances in protein folding since AlphaF

todos.content: Identify new protein folding models since AlphaFold 3 (e.g., RoseTTAFold improvements, ESMFold)
Analyze advances in predicting protein complexes and interactions
Explore hybrid methods integrating experimental and computational data
Investigate advances in modeling protein dynamics and flexibility
todos.active_form: Investigating advances in modeling dynamics and flexibility
